Package com.teamten.chess

Class Summary
Board Represents a chess board and the pieces on it.
ComputerPlayer Plays chess.
ComputerPlayer.EvaluatedMove Stores a move and its score.
Game Records an entire game.
Move Stores a move in a chess game and its inverse.
Piece Represents a piece of a type and color.
PieceType Represents a type of piece, such as a queen or rook, but not of a particular color.
Side Sides are represented as an integer, with 0 for white and 1 for black.
 

Exception Summary
IllegalMoveException Thrown when a user tries to make a move that's not valid or legal.
